{"tid":367483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"耳後淋巴發炎","createTime":"2017-08-20T18:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T04:48:36.000Z","uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a05e95c72e87789959ec7e247ec4682f7d1ce429","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"我上網查過啲人一般都係想睇醫生食抗生素。粒嘢細咗但都唔斷尾，更有資料話要去醫院切咗佢可以斷尾。<br />\n想問大家有無經驗，我而家無掂佢，只要郁下都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1af9b512624ef9957a02b31cf4c54471eaff55f","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上網查過啲人一般都係睇醫生食抗生素。粒嘢細咗但都唔斷尾，更有資料話要去醫院切咗佢可以斷尾。<br />\n想問大家有無經驗，我而家無掂佢，只要郁下都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無個想字 打錯"},{"pid":"e1ad3df55d55719af29bd666218c0afd6baa17ce","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d346383a518e0f43fc835cc2ebeabe06aef3b4","tid":367483,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T20:49:53.000Z","msg":"睇醫生食抗生素睇咗兩三次先好"},{"pid":"6a620b5f346da9e9d434a1ae233af3e35debd855","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生食抗生素睇咗兩三次先好</blockquote><br />\n大概幾耐到呀"},{"pid":"3cbffee6654447eeaf6d140c8c76e93b35d2772c","tid":367483,"uid":75583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:16:30.000Z","msg":"我好似係感冒菌上咗淋巴，個時斷斷續續食咗成個月藥反反覆覆咁，後來去旅行，一離開香港就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e29c499bea0543bf0f0ed098f5a7e5520e94359","tid":367483,"uid":116563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"我都有淋巴核幾年啦 (耳後淋巴）<br />\n會隨著唔夠訓 食熱氣野<br />\n佢就會大左 下火後會細返<br />\n<br />\n發現果時食過一個月類固醇，都清唔到 <br />\n醫生就話無得斷尾<br />\n有驚過病變，佢話變癌會發大 紅腫 等等唔同病徵。<br />\n我都搵緊方法斷尾/ 通返淋巴"},{"pid":"e530b0ab980c7e60fdd71f26110e673530b20059","tid":367483,"uid":116563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"我係㩒落去先痛"},{"pid":"96dfc4bb398f4d984f86342f027d423f19798986","tid":367483,"uid":60628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"耳後有淋巴係正常的<br />\n唔使切<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.slidesharecdn.com%2Fexaminationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747%2F95%2Fexamination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg%3Fcb%3D1475044084&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3Lp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=87f51a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有痛/發大就唔正常<br />\n咁就要視乎咩野原因"},{"pid":"5ff4bc6620129cb3e41c1402da92561872a640ff","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"我無紅 但係係熱同腫"},{"pid":"8d97697092211fa153f595679a32ee666c862519","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"其實我兩三年前曾經都生過，不過個時唔知以為係一般瘡見好耐未消就拮爆咗，都反覆擠咗幾次先無咗粒嘢。<br />\n今次痛過上次先擔心，有見話係上次清唔曬會成日翻發，好想斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c909d360253167d7df42c09f8e277bf64f2f1522","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耳後有淋巴係正常的<br />\n唔使切<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.slidesharecdn.com%2Fexaminationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747%2F95%2Fexamination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg%3Fcb%3D1475044084&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3Lp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=87f51a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有痛/發大就唔正常<br />\n咁就要視乎咩野原因</blockquote><br />\n我粒嘢係耳珠後面對上個耳骨位，好似同圖中唔同？"},{"pid":"5aebeebf210b63ff0141cdff68525f066ebbb1de","tid":367483,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>耳後有淋巴係正常的<br />\n唔使切<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.slidesharecdn.com%2Fexaminationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747%2F95%2Fexamination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg%3Fcb%3D1475044084&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3Lp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=87f51a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有痛/發大就唔正常<br />\n咁就要視乎咩野原因</blockquote><br />\n我粒嘢係耳珠後面對上個耳骨位，好似同圖中唔同？</blockquote><br />\nSorry好似講得唔清楚，總之係耳仔後面條罅耳珠上小小，唔係圖中隔離咁樣"},{"pid":"6143c1f3f694791f39f432ad72ea90c25162e566","tid":367483,"uid":60628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>耳後有淋巴係正常的<br />\n唔使切<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.slidesharecdn.com%2Fexaminationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747%2F95%2Fexamination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg%3Fcb%3D1475044084&d=kPn1gkqpeMzuzWyn%2BST3Lp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=87f51a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://image.slidesharecdn.com/examinationoflymphnodesofheadandneck-160928062747/95/examination-of-lymph-nodes-of-head-and-neck-15-638.jpg?cb=1475044084</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有痛/發大就唔正常<br />\n咁就要視乎咩野原因</blockquote><br />\n我粒嘢係耳珠後面對上個耳骨位，好似同圖中唔同？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人位置唔一定完全一樣<br />\n同埋有d人多d，有d人少d"}]}